{{Reflist}}

{{WCW Championships}}
{{WCW World Television Championship}}

{{featured list}}

[[Category:World Championship Wrestling championships]]
[[Category:Television wrestling championships]]

The '''MTV Europe Music Award for Best Electronic''' was originally entitled '''Best Dance''' and was first awarded in [[1994 in music|1994]] until [[2003 in music|2003]]. It was one of the original two genre categories that were added to the MTV Europe Music Awards that year. The big winner on this category were [[The Prodigy]] with four awards. The category was revived in 2012, in which it was renamed to its current title.
==Winners and nominees== Winners are listed first and highlighted in '''bold'''.
